item.content:encoded:
header#masthead {
    padding: 30px 0;
}
.single-docs #post p {
	margin-bottom: 30px;
}
aside.widget-area {
    display: none !important;
}
.ezd-login-form-wrap {
    background: #fff;
    padding: 0 15px;
}
.ezd-login-form-wrap span{
	display: inline-block;
    font-size: 14px;
    margin: 7px 0;
    line-height: 17px;
    color: var(--ezd_brand_color);
    font-weight: 500;
}

.single-content p img.mp-loader {
	display: none;
}

input#mp_email {
    width: 400px;
}

body.body_dark .documentation_area_sticky.fullscreen-layout .ezd-container-fluid{
background:#131417 !important;
}

ul.sub-menu {
    padding-left: 0;
}

.site-header .header-image {
	max-width: 80px;
}

.search_form_wrap .search_submit_btn {
    margin: 0;
}

body.body_dark .documentation_area_sticky.fullscreen-layout .ezd-container-fluid{
background:#131417 !important;
}

/* .postid-8753  .doc_rightsidebar {
    padding-top: 110px;
}

.postid-8753 .doc_documentation_area.body_fixed .doc_left_sidebarlist.one-page-docs-sidebar-wrap {
    padding-top: 110px;
} */

You can configure the footer area of the theme from the settings option. You will find all relevant section settings to the "Footer" option. Navigate to <strong>Theme Options &gt; Footer Settings </strong>to go to this settings section. We provided all necessary instructions and descriptions with all the options.

<a href="https://wordpress-theme.spider-themes.net/docy/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/footer-2.png"><img class="alignnone wp-image-2192 size-full" src="https://wordpress-theme.spider-themes.net/docy/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/footer-2.png" alt="" width="1313" height="623" /></a>

&nbsp;

Go to <em><strong><span style="color: #000000;">Appearance &gt; Customize &gt; Site Identity</span>.</strong></em> Then Select an image as site icon. It's recommended to use a <strong><em>.ico</em></strong> image as the site icon (favicon).

<a href="https://wordpress-theme.spider-themes.net/docy/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/favicon-2.png"><img class="alignnone wp-image-2218 size-full" src="https://wordpress-theme.spider-themes.net/docy/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/favicon-2.png" alt="" width="461" height="501" /></a>

&nbsp;

